==========================
USAGE
==========================

Requires gstreamer:
sudo apt-get install gstreamer-tools 
sudo apt-get install libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev libgstreamer0.10-dev libglib2.0-dev 
sudo apt-get install libgtk2.0-dev 

and GSVideo library which I downloaded from http://sourceforge.net/projects/gsvideo/files/gsvideo/1.0/

Change line 15 for the video device you're using: 

  video = new GSCapture(this, ancho, alto, 10, "/dev/video0"); //linux

